    "body": "After Flashinfer API update, the backend chooses between cuDNN and CUTLASS depending on CUDA and cudnn version, so unsetting it does not mean it's always cuDNN.\r\n\r\nCurrently we use CUTLASS from Flashinfer\r\n\r\nSee https://docs.flashinfer.ai/generated/flashinfer.gemm.mm_fp4.html\r\n\r\nThe relevant shapes for Deepseek (w/ `python sgl-kernel/benchmark/bench_fp4_gemm.py`)\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1721\" height=\"1104\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a1dafad5-c3e4-46c8-82b5-8e670818e764\" />\r\n<img width=\"1721\" height=\"1104\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2e1c1359-def4-4d7f-967d-f5ca02e0932d\" />\r\n<img width=\"1721\" height=\"1104\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2f2bdb0d-8695-436b-bbda-826a5456e330\" />\r\n<img width=\"1721\" height=\"1104\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/95696a86-9ea2-4f0b-9762-8aa91a0b43fd\" />\r\n<img width=\"1783\" height=\"1104\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e4b7019a-86a8-46e7-9ac8-6686945ba9e9\" />\r\n<img width=\"1721\" height=\"1104\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f1c28442-8334-411f-b423-b2ad0d5e5d33\" />\r\n<img width=\"1721\" height=\"1104\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/4098540e-8cde-45a0-8000-b94de37361cb\" />\r\n<img width=\"1721\" height=\"1104\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c4331dd7-2e07-47a9-adc1-0c9290020805\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
